{"tid":1269403,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"長期抗爭第一步: 盡量不違法少交稅俾呢個殖民政府","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T07:23:23.000Z","uid":68080,"like":78,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bae25c6e5b41eefd8e66855c7f55fdef489cbf","tid":1269403,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"我相信大家都知道我地交既稅大部分都講會攞黎起大白象或者裝備狗鎮壓無辜市民<br />\n如果大家對於呢筆稅金既用途唔滿意 其實我地可以長期用好多手段黎avoid tax<br />\n以下我將會拋磚 希望大家come up更多既idea 大家一齊做不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少我希望我交既稅唔係用黎起明日大愚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭盔: 呢個唔係教大家逃稅係避稅 係合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n認可慈善捐款，其實由intern開始，我盡量都每個月十一奉獻，將自己人工既十分之一捐俾慈善機構，希望回饋社會。<br />\n當然我係all in無國界醫生，因為同中共關係最細，被貪污既機會都最細，救既人價值亦最大。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/salaries/allowances/deductions/approveddonation.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Ftaxes%2Fsalaries%2Fallowances%2Fdeductions%2Fapproveddonation.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=6e44ad1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/taxes/salaries/allowances/deductions/approveddonation.htm</a><br />\n而係香港稅制黎講，35%既taxable income其實都可以offset by charitable donation，而無國界醫生就係其中一個選擇。<br />\n講真我寧願射俾無國界醫生救非洲人都唔想交稅起明日大愚或者養班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於我既情況黎講，salary tax應該都可以cover到一段日子。<br />\n希望大家拋磚可以等我有更多方法，甚至避埋rates(呢個直頭講明養狗)<br />\n<br />\n當然希望大家係合法做事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日見<br />\n聽講有外國學者會係波斯富街同軍器廠街數人頭，希望大家盡量唔好打尖</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a097a82de9cf18dcbfe64352f2aba846eadef11","tid":1269403,"uid":196924,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"確實<br />\n喺漸進稅率之下<br />\n少35% taxable income, 隨時交少超過50%稅"},{"pid":"3cd2518c9948c78cd5186ef60a884138bb67bbd8","tid":1269403,"uid":68080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:17:07.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n我相信大家都唔想dup錢落海<br />\n俾呢個殖民政府射你既血汗錢上去送中"},{"pid":"04e4ff7763655a3905f135527c231e833b9607da","tid":1269403,"uid":34872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a097a82de9cf18dcbfe64352f2aba846eadef11","tid":1269403,"uid":196924,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"確實<br />\n喺漸進稅率之下<br />\n少35% taxable income, 隨時交少超過50%稅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"等睇佢下年轉玩法冇曬donation 同其他deduction<br />\n呢個政府癲起上黎冇野做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8427f616e7bfb11e8f0da434bc0dce95f6d7432","tid":1269403,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"射落海 都唔比你政府<br />\n<br />\n何況係射去做善事 &nbsp; 一定要捐!"},{"pid":"d386cd4ab44db502f5fbeb34e4ce89d2af9b5619","tid":1269403,"uid":68080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04e4ff7763655a3905f135527c231e833b9607da","tid":1269403,"uid":34872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a097a82de9cf18dcbfe64352f2aba846eadef11","tid":1269403,"uid":196924,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:10:37.000Z","msg":"確實<br />\n喺漸進稅率之下<br />\n少35% taxable income, 隨時交少超過50%稅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"等睇佢下年轉玩法冇曬donation 同其他deduction<br />\n呢個政府癲起上黎冇野做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"be water<br />\n下年得 再下一年唔得<br />\n一定有其他方法<br />\n做得一年係一年"},{"pid":"95fd592df282bb9afe54b1c485f30a7f032d0bc0","tid":1269403,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply